[SN]TITLE[SN]
First Brit with bionic leg brace

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man from London has become the first Briton to walk with the help of a bionic leg brace.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is unsupported on your device
5 February 2015 Last updated at 09:07 GMT
John Simpson wasn't able to walk without help before being fitted with the C-brace.
It uses a built-in computer and sensors to allow the knee to control walking.
John says: "It's going to change my life."
